### 1. Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

###

### 2. Register
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@devispro.de",
  "password": "motdepasse123",
  "company": "Klempnerei Test",
  "lang": "de"
}

###

### 3. Login → copie le token reçu !
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@devispro.de",
  "password": "motdepasse123"
}

###

### 4. Me (remplace TON_TOKEN par le token reçu au login)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwiZW1haWwiOiJ0ZXN0QGRldmlzcHJvLmRlIiwiY29tcGFueSI6IktsZW1wbmVyZWkgVGVzdCIsImlhdCI6MTc3NzQ1NjIyNCwiZXhwIjoxNzc4MDYxMDI0fQ.hvFijjdVTM86oFnL22oaGPDmMzGBoFQOUlyghpv8GNk

###

### 5. Créer un devis
POST http://localhost:3001/api/devis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwiZW1haWwiOiJ0ZXN0QGRldmlzcHJvLmRlIiwiY29tcGFueSI6IktsZW1wbmVyZWkgVGVzdCIsImlhdCI6MTc3NzQ1NjIyNCwiZXhwIjoxNzc4MDYxMDI0fQ.hvFijjdVTM86oFnL22oaGPDmMzGBoFQOUlyghpv8GNk

